---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Accessibility" description="Accessibility statement for UK Elections.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Accessibility</p>
    <h1>Readable, keyboard-accessible election data.</h1>
  </section>
  <section class="section prose-block">
    <p>The scaffold uses semantic HTML, visible focus states, high-contrast text, and a skip link. Interactive lookup and charting features will be tested before launch.</p>
    <p>Known limitation: the live data explorer is not yet built, so its accessibility cannot be assessed.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
